name: Adventure's of Túlio & Tiba #1
description: Túlio: A crazy human. Tiba: Unknown Creature. They are always together for reasons that no one knows (including me). In this episode, they were surprised by the archrival "Douglas, the Demon", while they were going to harvest fruits.  "Adventure's of Túlio & Tiba" is my new series, produced in VR. The first page was created using Gravity Sketch + Blender.  WiW (May 4, 2021).
